docs.text: 👋 Welcome to My GitHub Profile! Hello! I’m Dominik Ocsofszki, a final-year Computer Science student at Bonn-Rhein-Sieg University of Applied Sciences. My GitHub repositories showcase a blend of academic projects, personal explorations, and open-source interests. 🌱 About Me 🧑‍🎓 Education: Final-year Computer Science student at Bonn-Rhein-Sieg University of Applied Sciences. 💻 Interests: Software development, language servers and technical problem-solving. 🛠 Skills: Proficient in Java, Python, JavaScript and TypeScript 🌐 Projects: Engaged in developing a LSP-compatible language server as part of my thesis. ⚡ Frameworks: Experienced with Angular and Spring Boot, with foundational knowledge in Docker, Node.js, PyTorch, and Vaadin. 🔧 Tools & Technologies: Enthusiast of NeoVim, Tree-Sitter, and the Language Server Protocol (LSP). 🔍 Other Knowledge: REST APIs, JSON, Bash/Zsh, jq, Jenkins, Maven, and Git.
